        "curveballHtml": "You've just sent your copy to the Creative Director. She messages back: <em>\"Good start. One thing: the CEO just saw the initial designs for the launch email and radio spot. She thinks they're too 'safe' for a relaunch. She wants more 'pop' and 'excitement' to grab the new B2C audience. She mentioned 'something a bit more modern, like what those new direct-to-consumer brands do.' She needs a revised approach for the email subject line and radio spot script ASAP.\"</em>",
