        "curveballHtml": "It's two days post-launch. You just got an urgent call from a pilot firm: <strong>Ask LexForge hallucinated a non-existent clause in a critical M&A document, causing their client to nearly miss a negotiation deadline.</strong> The lawyer caught it, but is furious. Your Head of Legal is demanding an immediate shutdown. The CTO wants to understand the scope before reacting.<br><br>The CEO's message: <em>\"What's our immediate next step? I need a clear path forward in 30 minutes for the leadership team.\"</em>",
