          "helperHtml": "List your top 3 action items. For each, specify a concrete action, a clear owner, a realistic deadline, and a priority (High/Medium). Group them by category (Prevent Recurrence, Improve Detection, Improve Response).",
          "structureTip": "Start each action item with a verb. Example: '1. Action: Implement automated CI gate for migrations. Owner: Platform Team. Deadline: EOY. Priority: High. Category: Prevent Recurrence.' Be specific.",
