        "curveballHtml": "You're about to present your postmortem. The CTO just messaged you: <em>\"I saw the 'review BI workload' action item from two weeks ago was never picked up. How do we explain that without assigning blame, but still ensuring accountability? This is exactly what I mean by stricter change management. What's your take before I present to the board?\"</em> She's looking for a candid, constructive answer.",
        "recapText": "My postmortem outlines the DB migration and BI query interaction as the root cause. Key actions include automated migration checks, better BI workload monitoring, and clearer DB troubleshooting in runbooks.",
