        "curveballHtml": "You've just presented your voice system proposal to the design-systems team. Right after, the Head of Product for the new, unlaunched product (launching in 4 months) comes to you. She says: <strong>\"My team needs a complete voice guide and component library for our new product in 6 weeks, not 4 months. We can't wait for a full system rollout. What are you doing to help us?\"</strong><br><br>Your design-systems partner looks at you, waiting for your lead.",
