        "curveballHtml": "You've just shared your recovery plan with the CMO. She responds: <em>\"Great plan. But I just saw our biggest competitor, MealMaven, launched a new 'AI-powered recipe generator' that's getting a lot of buzz. We need to build one too, ASAP. Can we pause some of these fixes and allocate engineering to that? We need quick wins to show the board.\"</em><br><br>You know this would divert critical resources from your core recovery.",
