        "curveballHtml": "You've just shared your 90-day plan with the CFO. She immediately forwards you a new BSI (German federal cyber agency) alert: <strong>'Urgent Advisory: Increased Ransomware Activity Targeting Healthcare Backup Systems.'</strong> It highlights unencrypted backups as a primary exploit vector for data exfiltration and destruction.<br><br>The CFO's message: <em>\"This BSI alert just came in. Our unencrypted backups finding is now public knowledge. Does this change our 90-day plan? Need your quick take before I finalize for the Audit Committee.\"</em>",
