          "text": "Don't panic and rewrite everything. Acknowledge the new, strong competitor, but don't assume it invalidates your program's value or your proposed strategy. Focus on what you can control: your program's unique strengths, your demonstrated learning, and your plan for improvement. Maintain composure and strategic thinking."
